## WHAT MAKES IT DIFFERENT (Category Definition)

### This Is Not Call Analytics

Call analytics tell you *what happened*.
Word Is Bond tells you *what stands*.

| They optimize conversations | We preserve them |
| --------------------------- | ---------------- |
| They summarize              | We certify       |
| They infer intent           | We record it     |
| They delete history         | We retain truth  |

We don’t grade your calls.
We **bind them**.

